{"word":"G3930 - παρέχω - paréchō - par-ekh'-o - Bring","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">παρέχω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">paréchō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">par-ekh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Bring</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - செய், கடைப்பிடி, ஊழியஞ்செய்"},{"paragraph":"1. to reach forth, offer"},{"paragraph":"2. to show, afford, supply"},{"paragraph":"3. to offer, show, or present oneself"},{"paragraph":"4. to exhibit or offer on one's own part"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3844 - παρά - pará - par-ah'/3844\">G3844</a> and <a href=\"#/G2192 - ἔχω - échō - ekh'-o/2192\">G2192</a>; to <i>hold near</i>, that is, <i>present</i>, <i>afford</i>, <i>exhibit</i>, <i>furnish occasion:</i> - bring, do, give, keep, minister, offer, shew, + trouble.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}